      "title": "Ape Jana Bala Party Chairman remanded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chairman of the Ape Jana Bala Party Saman Perera who was arrested by the Tangalle Police for harbouring a murder suspect was remanded till August 31 by the Tangale magistrate's Court.",
        "The 46-year-old suspect, a resident of Kosgoda was arrested yesterday in connection with aiding and abetting a suspect connected to a murder took place in Kaduwela on June 5."
